@startuml Product State Machine
title Product Lifecycle - State Machine Diagram
left to right direction

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor#F3E5F5
    BorderColor#7B1FA2
    ArrowColor#424242
}

[*] --> DRAFT : Manager/Admin creates product

DRAFT --> ACTIVE : Publish product\n(Auto-activate if stock > 0)
DRAFT --> OUT_OF_STOCK : Publish with zero stock

ACTIVE --> OUT_OF_STOCK : Stock reaches 0
ACTIVE --> INACTIVE : Manager deactivates
ACTIVE --> DELETED : Soft delete by Admin

OUT_OF_STOCK --> ACTIVE : Stock replenished
OUT_OF_STOCK --> INACTIVE : Manager deactivates
OUT_OF_STOCK --> DELETED : Soft delete by Admin

INACTIVE --> ACTIVE : Manager activates\n(stock > 0)
INACTIVE --> OUT_OF_STOCK : Manager activates\n(stock = 0)
INACTIVE --> DELETED : Soft delete by Admin

DELETED --> [*] : Permanent deletion\n(after 30 days)

DELETED --> ACTIVE : Restore product\n(Admin only)

' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' NOTES
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note right of ACTIVE
  Visible in catalog
  Available for purchase
  Inventory tracked
  Searchable
end note

note right of OUT_OF_STOCK
  Visible in catalog
  Not purchasable
  "Out of Stock" badge
  Notify when available
end note

note right of INACTIVE
  Hidden from catalog
  Not purchasable
  Maintains history
  Can be restored
end note

note right of DELETED
  Soft deleted
  Data retained 30 days
  Can be restored
  Hard delete after period
end note

@enduml
